      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in strictly as-is condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be roadworthy. The exterior shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust on the wheel arches, several deep dents, and clear coat failure on the hood and roof. Mechanically, the engine suffers from a persistent misfire and the transmission shifts harshly, while the interior has significant tearing in the upholstery and a pervasive musty odor. This car is best suited as a project for an experienced mechanic or as a source for spare parts.",
