    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape, running smoothly and looking great. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s ready for plenty more adventures. If you're looking for something reliable and well-loved, this is the one for you\u2014come check it out!",
      "price": 32500.0,
