    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This A80-generation Supra Turbo is a mechanically sound example of Toyota\u2019s flagship performance engineering. At its heart is the 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six, featuring a sequential forced induction system that delivers a broad torque curve and exceptional throttle response. Power is routed through the coveted Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox to a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal traction and corner-exit stability. The suspension retains its original double-wishbone geometry, offering precise kinematic feedback. While the car shows signs of use appropriate for its age, the drivetrain remains tight, the boost pressure is consistent, and the four-piston braking system provides confident deceleration with no fade. This is a robust, analog machine ready for the open road.",
